{"tid":1757441,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非又好，勇武派又好可唔可以入嚟睇一睇！","createTime":"2019-11-26T13:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T16:03:54.000Z","uid":12653,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4e96afd5885a8f8f69116732de68691b4342b5","tid":1757441,"uid":12653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:44:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我求下你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n剛才我接觸完一個想自殺嘅年輕人<br />\n佢係因為社會事加上其他因素所以有咁嘅念頭<br />\n雖然社會抗爭並非係唯一嘅因素<br />\n<br />\n但係我喺呢度懇請大家喺度爭論用咩方式繼續抗爭嘅時候<br />\n和理非既post也好，勇武派既post也好<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以喺往後日子嘅行動都表明一句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">心理狀態感到有壓力唔理想嘅巴打絲打可以休息一下先！我哋做埋你嗰份！唔好覺得有壓力！</span></span>之類既說話<br />\n<br />\n因為依家就係有好多年輕人覺得自己點解被捕嘅唔係我，我好冇用之類嘅想法！<br />\n<br />\n明明狀態已經唔好，唔好係呢啲氛圍底下再迫佢哋出嚟啦"},{"pid":"2d57e9a4cc180daf1c1be9df1d90ab9f5bb99a91","tid":1757441,"uid":127494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:45:11.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"48e7848c8653815ae43018670f4df72ee5aeede6","tid":1757441,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:48:15.000Z","msg":"大家都好怕自己唔出就會無晒人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bff952f8fe7f9ae31e67d73973b190880dd3f5","tid":1757441,"uid":12653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48e7848c8653815ae43018670f4df72ee5aeede6","tid":1757441,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:48:15.000Z","msg":"大家都好怕自己唔出就會無晒人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:48:55.000Z","msg":"就係呢啲想法迫死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4bca216269efd13b403fa763e6d654b0216b931","tid":1757441,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"休息下唔係罪"},{"pid":"e4a69570937826c96da1dc8a0bf9700a6207b